import { createApp } from 'vue'
import App from './App.vue'
import  '@/assets/bootstrap/bootstrap.min.css'
import '@/assets/bootstrap/style-cv.css'
import bg from '@/assets/js/bg-animated.vue'
import trigger from'@/assets/js/skills-animation.js'

createApp(App).mount('#app')

createApp(trigger).mount('#trigger')
